content: Had an insightful session with my mentor. We're now planning a series of workshops to fine-tune our AI-human collaboration approach. It's about making tech a sidekick, not the hero, in our decision-making process.

Just got word that our patent application is looking good. The legal team is confident we've covered all the bases. It's a relief, but also a reminder of how much work has gone into this. Next steps, here we come.
